data.description:
Are you looking for the perfect blend of rural living and convenience? Look no further! This beautiful 4 bedroom (1 non conforming) 1.5 bath home is sitting on a corner lot of 2.5 acres, giving you plenty of room to spread out and make it your own. Just minutes away from I-49, this location offers the best of both worlds - peaceful country living with easy access to amenities and attractions in town. 

You'll love the modern updates throughout, including newer roof, vinyl siding, vinyl windows, heat & air and fresh flooring. And if that weren't enough to sweeten the deal there's also a new 32x52 detached shop with lean-to so you can store all your tools and toys! Don't miss out on this amazing opportunity - call now for more information or to schedule a showing!
